<p>
  <span class="nym">Bertha</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>beraht</i>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>berht</i> 'bright' from <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*berhtaz</i>.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of numerous early saints.  The name of two queens of France (10th C, 11th C), a Byzantine empress (12th C), and a queen of Burgundy (10th C).</p>
</div>
  
  
  


